Brooke Vincent https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brooke_Vincent 0 Brooke Vincent (born 4 June 1992) is an English actress. She is known for her portrayal of Sophie Webster in the ITV soap-opera Coronation Street since 2004 where she took over the role from Emma Woodward.
